WEBVTT



00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.016
Hello, this is John Piper, and I want to update you on the content of this sermon podcast today.

00:00:05.984 --> 00:00:10.560
Back when it started, I was the only teacher at Desiring God.

00:00:10.304 --> 00:00:15.200
And I was still preaching week in and week out at Bethlehem Baptist Church.

00:00:15.712 --> 00:00:17.952
But since 2013,

00:00:17.920 --> 00:00:20.448
I stepped away from the pastorate

00:00:20.288 --> 00:00:22.592
And now work full-time

00:00:22.336 --> 00:00:24.128
At desiring God.

00:00:24.512 --> 00:00:28.160
So we established a team of teachers.

00:00:28.448 --> 00:00:37.184
since i'm preaching less these days, maybe ten or fifteen times a year at various conferences and chapels and services.

00:00:37.504 --> 00:00:40.096
And the Desiring God team,

00:00:39.872 --> 00:00:42.016
Is preaching more and more

00:00:42.144 --> 00:00:46.624
We want to update this podcast with a new name, a new visual.

00:00:46.432 --> 00:00:47.840
Presentation,

00:00:47.776 --> 00:00:52.960
To reflect this new reality at desire in God and to include

00:00:52.800 --> 00:00:54.176
Messages

00:00:54.016 --> 00:00:55.520
From our other

00:00:55.296 --> 00:00:56.928
Teachers on the team

00:00:57.216 --> 00:00:58.912
I commend them to you.

00:00:59.040 --> 00:01:01.376
I know these men. I trust them.

00:01:01.216 --> 00:01:02.912
I admire them.

00:01:02.976 --> 00:01:05.440
They have remarkable gifts.

00:01:05.824 --> 00:01:11.552
I believe you will find their messages to be a wonderful, rich, God-centered,

00:01:11.200 --> 00:01:13.824
Fountain of biblical truth

00:01:13.632 --> 00:01:16.864
With the flavor of Christian hedonism,

00:01:16.768 --> 00:01:19.744
that we love so much here at Desiring God.
